import React from 'react';
import {
  Box,
  Paper,
  Typography,
  Container,
  Grid,
  Card,
  CardContent,
} from '@mui/material';

const BlankPage = () => {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ mt: 4, mb: 4 }}>
      <Grid container spacing={3}>
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Paper sx={{ p: 3 }}>
            <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
              Welcome to CRM Dashboard
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
              This is your starting point for managing customer relationships.
            </Typography>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>
        
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                Quick Actions
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                Add customers, manage leads, and track interactions all in one place.
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                Recent Activity
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                View your latest customer interactions and updates.
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default BlankPage;
